Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:28.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ ガキが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:30.48,Default,Sakamoto,0,0,0,,Damn. I can't get it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:29.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…っと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:30.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,んごっ うっと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:32.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ この
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:34.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ とれねーぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:35.02,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,There is no point.
