Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:25.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買ってみたんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:27.74,Default,Yukko,0,0,0,,Does it look good?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:27.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,似合う？
